Solutions









At SCM Connections, we have the experience to create lasting solutions for every facet of your Supply Chain. Think of us as your one stop shop; From Demand to Supply and even Collaboration, the SCM Connections team has it covered.Integrated Business Planning


Putting it All Together






Integrated Decision Making







Speed = Good







Data Integrity







Profits - We Like Those







Learn More: Ebook







Whoa!  Sales AND Operations?  That meeting cannot go well.  Wait, they’re all supposed to agree on a common plan?  Have you ever seen what those meetings are like?  SCM Connections has, and we know what it takes to make them successful.  We know it’s not just a meeting, it’s a never ending process, and we mean that in a good way.  To really get S&OP planning right it needs to be a constant, focused effort that becomes a part of how you do business.  And SCM Connections has the deep supply chain and technology expertise that can get you there.






With SAP and HANA the supply chain processes can be much more productive.  The ability to generate detailed analysis of alternatives on the fly, is a powerful tool that speeds the decision making process dramatically.  Questions can be answered in real time and scenarios evaluated just as quickly.  SCM Connections can use their technical wizardry to develop the process and configure the solution to provide instant answers as soon as they are asked.  In this on demand world, speed is key, and SCM Connections delivers






One source of the truth.  Sure it sounds nice, but it’s much harder to pull off than it seems.  When everyone shows up to an S&OP meeting with their own reports, it becomes impossible to know who’s “right”.  What makes IBP on HANA different is that everyone operates from the same bits and bytes, capacity projections, inventory values and all .
 
It’s a big change to incorporate in the day to day supply chain process and SCM Connections is an industry leader that can get you real time data that’s right the first time. The best way to avoid conflicting information is to avoid bringing conflicting information.  SCM Connections can work will all areas of the business to develop the right set of reports to meet the common goals of each and every aspect of the planning process.






IBP doesn’t just allow you to see numbers faster, it generates better numbers faster. The ability to generate simulations that maximize profits and evaluate different scenarios in real time is  dream of every supply chain officer, and SCM Connections can help you make that dream a reality.  The IBP platform from SAP allows the flexible and integrated planning tools that look across all aspects of the organization to help you find the optimal scenario that meets everyone’s needs  And it the end their profit maximization tools make all the difference to you, your stakeholders and eventually your wallet.







