Demand


Predicting the Future… Today!






Be the Town Crier







Be Less Wrong







Any Level, Any Time







Service with a Scalpel







Link the conversations between sales, marketing, finance and operations to make sure everyone is on the same page.  When teams communicate beautiful things can happen.  Products are ready to support promotions, financial plans are there to fund the business, surprises start to disappear.






Forecasts are wrong, let’s not kid ourselves.  But let’s try to be less wrong!  Ok that’s not really a great rallying cry, but a solid demand planning foundation supported by a predictable and repeatable planning process can do wonders.  Find the weak spots, let the tools do the heavy lifting, and communicate, communicate, communicate.  That’s how SCMC does demand planning






Don’t be confined by pre-configured aggregates.  Plan at whatever level you please with IBP demand.  Seems like a small thing but it has immense implications.  Looking at the data from any angle any time you want allows the average planner to seem like an genius, and geniuses to seem extra-genius-y.






Who doesn’t love customer service?  Not us!  We also love double negatives.  But especially we love your customers.  IBP demand allows you to slice and dice data to the customer, product, region, shipping point or receiving point.  That’s the ability to target service where it has the most impact.






